<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，巴斯家的孩子们感觉好多了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们依然非常想念自己的父母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的爸爸妈妈已经离开一周了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当然，他们每晚都会打电话过来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这跟爸爸妈妈真的在身边还是不一样的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望妈妈和爸爸能快点儿回来。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太想念他们了。”简说。她都快哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸得先找到工作。”赛伊勇敢地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>实际上，在他心里，他也很想念爸爸妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望他今天就能找到工作。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这几个孩子几乎是同时抬起了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们想的是不是和我一样？”赛伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“休伊。”鲍比小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们不能再许愿了。”潘瑟分辨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们每个人都许过两个愿了。结束了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这次不一样。”赛伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不是为了我们。这是为了妈妈和爸爸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们思考着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且我们还没有向休伊告别呢。”简补充道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说的对。”潘瑟承认了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，孩子们又一次出发去见休伊了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和往常一样把木桶降到了井底，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他用了更长时间才找到休伊的壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最终，赛伊找到了休伊并把他拉了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你躲在哪儿了，休伊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个神奇生物出现的时候赛伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是忙一些事情。”休伊回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他避开了孩子们的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊看上去和他以前的样子有点儿不同了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但孩子们不敢问他遇到了什么事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天轮到谁了？”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他恢复了平常的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看看彼此，然后赛伊回答说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，这是我们大家的愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着自己的兄弟姐妹还有自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊看上去很吃惊：“这很少见啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那你们的愿望是什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们希望爸爸能找到工作。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后快点回家。”简补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你们知道规矩的。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他盯着孩子们发愣的脸：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“愿望的有效期只有一天，还记得吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他提醒他们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是啊。”他们伤心地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这真的是我们最最想实现的愿望啊。”鲍比恳求说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其它愿望都是为了好玩儿。这个是真的愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对啊，这个是真正的愿望。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊慢慢地摇摇头：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很抱歉，孩子们，但规矩就是规矩。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的鳍开始闪烁光芒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次的颜色比以往都要多，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但孩子们太伤心了，都没有注意到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，休伊。我们明白了。”最后，赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们就没有别的愿望了。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊轻轻地将休伊放回了木桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开心点吧。”休伊说，“我敢肯定，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们的爸爸妈妈很快就回家了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完这句话，休伊就消失在了他的壳里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊再一次将他送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们带着沉重的心走回了家，脸色也很难看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道什么能让咱们高兴起来。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们坐在门廊里吃着零食。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该为每个人烤点饼干。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”鲍比问。他的嘴里塞满了花生酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，在遇到休伊之后，发生了这么多事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟继续说，“我们的愿望影响了其他人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨、贝克尔先生和西尔弗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简数着数，“还有农夫詹金斯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且我们交了很多朋友。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这想法不错。”赛伊开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，孩子们烤了很多饼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当然，玛莎阿姨和兰姆也帮了忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>屋外天色开始变暗了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以明天拿这些饼干去送给每个人。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，响起了敲门声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去开门。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在想会是谁呢？”鲍比一边问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>364054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一边又从盘子里拿了一块饼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>364055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“惊喜哦！”两个熟悉的声音大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>369097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>374578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是妈妈和爸爸，他们回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>